{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Game Klasik Favorit “Secret of Mana” Mendapatkan Treatment Remake Modern","content":"<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Square Enix. Siapa bro sis gamers yang tidak mengenal nama sebesar ini?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Walau terkenal sebagai pabriknya game-game RPG berkualitas tinggi tapi sepertinya mayoritas gamers (terutama yang tidak mengenal/mengikuti sepak terjang Squaresoft di era 16 &amp; 32-Bit) hanya mengenal beberapa judul saja dari Square.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ambil contoh misalnya <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/final-fantasy-vii-bukan-final-fantasy-yang-terbaik-tapi-paling-fenomenal/\">Final Fantasy VII</a> atau <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/wow-final-fantasy-xv-hadir-dalam-versi-pc-dan-smartphone/\">Final Fantasy XV</a>. Gamers modern tentu mengenal kedua judul besar ini. Final Fantasy merupakan franchise besar RPG dari Square Enix yang sudah berusia lebih dari 30 tahun    [<a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kejutan-di-gala-event-final-fantasy-30th-anniversary-exhibition/\">Kejutan di Gala Event Final Fantasy 30th Anniversary Exhibition]</a>. Berkat Final Fantasy pula nama Square melambung tinggi ke jajaran elites developer/publisher dunia. Apalagi ditambah merger mereka dengan Enix, yang juga super populer dengan franchise RPG mereka sendiri seperti Dragon Quest ataupun Star Ocean, menjadikan Square Enix raksasa game RPG dunia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42992\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42992\" data-attachment-id=\"42992\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dragon Quest konon lebih populer lagi di Jepang ketimbang Final Fantasy. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dragon Quest konon lebih populer lagi di Jepang ketimbang Final Fantasy. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42992\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3.jpg\" alt=\"Dragon Quest konon lebih populer lagi di Jepang ketimbang Final Fantasy. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42992\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dragon Quest konon lebih populer lagi di Jepang ketimbang Final Fantasy. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi Square Enix tidak melulu soal Final Fantasy. Atau Dragon Quest. Ada setumpuk judul game Square Enix lainnya; baik saat mereka masih berupa Squaresoft maupun Enix. Salah satu dari begitu banyak game Squaresoft adalah “Seiken Densetsu 聖剣伝説 ”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_43000\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43000\" data-attachment-id=\"43000\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden. Sumber gambar: amazon.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden. Sumber gambar: amazon.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43000\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11.jpg\" alt=\"Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden. Sumber gambar: amazon.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43000\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden. Sumber gambar: amazon.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dirilis untuk platform Game Boy di Jepang tahun 1991 dengan judul “Seiken Densetsu – Final Fantasy Gaiden 聖剣伝説 ～ファイナルファンタジー外伝～ / Holy Sword Legend: Final Fantasy Side Story”, game action RPG ini mirip game Nintendo “The Legend of Zelda” namun dengan mekanisme khas RPG seperti levelling dan HP/MP. Karena merupakan ‘cerita sampingan’ untuk Final Fantasy maka elemen khas dari Final Fantasy seperti Chocobo juga muncul disana. Tapi dalam perjalanannya, game Seiken Densetsu mampu melepaskan diri dari bayang-bayang Final Fantasy dan menjadi <em>franchise</em> sendiri. Yaitu “The Mana” series.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42998\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42998\" data-attachment-id=\"42998\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden screenshot. Sumber gambar: gramunion.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden screenshot. Sumber gambar: gramunion.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42998\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9.jpg\" alt=\"Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden screenshot. Sumber gambar: gramunion.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42998\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden screenshot. Sumber gambar: gramunion.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Saat dijual di Amerika dan Eropa, Seiken Densetsu mengalami perubahan judul (dan sedikit alterasi/perubahan di plot) menjadi “Final Fantasy Adventure” dan “Final Fantasy Mystic Quest”. Ini memang biasa terjadi untuk game Jepang saat dirilis di luar Jepang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42999\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42999\" data-attachment-id=\"42999\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Versi Amerika Seiken Densetsu. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Versi Amerika Seiken Densetsu. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42999\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10.jpg\" alt=\"Versi Amerika Seiken Densetsu. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42999\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Versi Amerika Seiken Densetsu. Sumber gambar: gamefaqs.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Seiken Densetsu kemudian berubah menjadi serial “Mana” untuk pasar di luar Jepang.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jika sekuel dari Seiken Densetsu dirilis untuk SNES/SuFami Jepang diberi judul “Seiken Densetsu 2 聖剣伝説 2 ”, maka di versi internasional game ini berjudul “Secret of Mana”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42996\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42996\" data-attachment-id=\"42996\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Game klasik favorit banyak gamers RPG. Sumber gambar: pinterest.comGame klasik favorit banyak gamers RPG. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Game klasik favorit banyak gamers RPG. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42996\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7.jpg\" alt=\"Game klasik favorit banyak gamers RPG. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42996\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Game klasik favorit banyak gamers RPG. Sumber gambar: pinterest.com</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42995\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42995\" data-attachment-id=\"42995\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Versi Amerika dari Seiken Densetsu 2. Sumber gambar: geekqc.ca\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Versi Amerika dari Seiken Densetsu 2. Sumber gambar: geekqc.ca&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42995\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6.jpg\" alt=\"Versi Amerika dari Seiken Densetsu 2. Sumber gambar: geekqc.ca\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42995\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Versi Amerika dari Seiken Densetsu 2. Sumber gambar: geekqc.ca</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Setelah Seiken Densetsu 2 / Secret of Mana, game <em>franchise</em> ‘Mana’ ini terus berlanjut.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Seiken Densetsu 3 聖剣伝説 3 ” dirilis tahun 1995 untuk SNES/SuFami. Tadinya game ini akan dirilis juga untuk pasar Amerika Serikat tapi berbagai masalah dan besarnya biaya untuk lokalisasi membuat Squaresoft angkat tangan dan membatalkan rencana tersebut.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game berikutnya dari ‘Mana’ series bisa muncul di pasar internasional melalui tangan dingin Sony dan PlayStation mereka. Di Jepang game tersebut diberi judul “Seiken Densetsu: Legend of Mana”, sementara di pasar internasional game ini dikenal dengan judul “Legend of Mana”. Itu terjadi di tahun 1999. Legend of Mana disutradarai langsung oleh kreator asli Seiken Densetsu, Koichi Ishii dengan musik ditangani oleh salah satu <em>maestro</em> musik game RPG dunia, Yoko Shimomura. Game PlayStation One ini sukses terjual 400.000 unit di minggu pertama penjualannya, terlepas dari kritik di bagian storyline yang dianggap lemah dan tidak sebagus game ‘Mana’ lain.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42991\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42991\" data-attachment-id=\"42991\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Seiken Densetsu pertama untuk 32-Bit. Sumber gambar: game-oldies.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Seiken Densetsu pertama untuk 32-Bit. Sumber gambar: game-oldies.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42991\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2.jpg\" alt=\"Seiken Densetsu pertama untuk 32-Bit. Sumber gambar: game-oldies.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42991\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Seiken Densetsu pertama untuk 32-Bit. Sumber gambar: game-oldies.com</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Franchise</em> ‘Mana’ memiliki cukup banyak game <em>spin-off</em> seperti misalnya “Children of Mana” (2005 | NDS). Ada juga “Dawn of Mana” (di Jepang diberi judul Seiken Densetsu 4 聖剣伝説 ”) yang dianggap <em>canonical</em> karena memakai judul dan nomer seri seperti Seiken Densetsu sebelumnya. Dawn of Mana dirilis tahun 2006 untuk PlayStation 2. Koichi Ishii kembali terlibat sebagai designer dan sutradara game. Sayang kesuksesan game ini tergolong biasa-biasa saja untuk ukuran game ‘Mana’ series karena hanya terjual 410.000 unit sampai akhir tahun 2008. Kebanyakan kritik ada di bagian sistem levelling dan kontrol yang dianggap menjengkelkan serta story yang tidak keren walau banyak pujian untuk grafis dan musiknya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42990\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42990\" data-attachment-id=\"42990\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"‘Mana’ game untuk PlayStation 2. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;‘Mana’ game untuk PlayStation 2. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42990\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1.jpg\" alt=\"‘Mana’ game untuk PlayStation 2. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-42990\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">‘Mana’ game untuk PlayStation 2. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mungkin karena dianggap sebagai yang paling sukses, Seiken Densetsu 2 kemudian di-remake oleh Square Enix untuk pasar RPG modern saat ini.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pasar Jepang yang pertama mendapatkan game remake tersebut. Tiga game pertama Seiken Densetsu (Seiken Densetsu: Final Fantasy Gaiden, Seiken Densetsu 2 &amp; Seiken Densetsu 3) digabung dalam satu game “Seiken Densetsu Collection” untuk Nintendo Switch dan dirilis tahun 2017 kemarin.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_42997\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-42997\" data-attachment-id=\"42997\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-klasik-favorit-secret-mana-mendapatkan-treatment-remake-modern/attachment/mana8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Spesial untuk pasar Jepang. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Spesial untuk pasar Jepang. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/mana8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42997\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/